parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the keyless start system can cause the vehicle to drain the battery, making it difficult or impossible to start the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle alarm sounds intermittently
the instrumental panel lights flicker
the vehicle attempts to start on its own
the backup camera is inoperable
and the vehicle is unable to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can cause a blind spot when reversing, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The backup camera display is black
the camera is inoperable
and the wiring harness is frayed or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Instrumental Panel and Dash System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrumental panel and dash system can cause the vehicle to malfunction, making it difficult to operate the vehicle safely.
symptoms: The instrumental panel lights flicker
the dash system freezes or restarts
and the alarm sounds intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Issues (Fuel Rail/System Pressure, Fuel Injectors, Fuel Pump)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system components can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become difficult to start, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the engine warning light comes on
the vehicle is difficult to start
the fuel pump fails
the fuel injectors fail
the fuel rail/system pressure is too low or too high.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Capless Fuel Filler System Issues (Water Intrusion, Ice Formation)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The capless fuel filler system can allow water to enter the fuel tank, causing ice to form and blocking the fuel filler neck, which can prevent the vehicle from being fueled and potentially lead to a life-threatening situation.
symptoms: The fuel filler door is frozen shut
water enters the fuel tank
ice forms in the fuel filler neck
the vehicle cannot be fueled
the fuel filler door is difficult to open.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Emissions System Issues (Emissions System Warning Light, Fuel Tank Replacement)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the emissions system can cause the vehicle to emit excessive pollutants, which can harm the environment and potentially cause health problems.
symptoms: The emissions system warning light comes on
the fuel tank needs to be replaced
the vehicle is emitting excessive pollutants.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tailgate wiring harness can cause the rear-view camera to malfunction, leading to a safety concern when reversing, potentially resulting in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear-view camera is inoperable
the camera screen is black
the camera wire is fractured or broken
the wiring harness is pinched or severed
the backup camera is not working properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in receiving parts for recall repairs can leave vehicles unrepaired, potentially leading to safety issues and accidents.
symptoms: The contact received notification of a recall
but the part to do the recall repair was unavailable
the manufacturer had exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair.
